  "title": "二次方募资在何种程度上可以资助思维工具的创作？",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"RymthN-2\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z5YhNc8HVKxjg9a3h3SeCyKqnNDFgiY6WGrM\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">思想工具</a>很难募资，这很大程度上是因为<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zXseK39g1SHgQvMXLbnaB1AUZ2WL5ffDzsbZ\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">新颖的用户界面创意是公共物品</a>。那么<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z6d3zr35eY2KeyrBAXQbsZ8cTTyTCdxWaBmcC\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">公共物品的二次方募资</a>是否可以解决这一问题？</p><p data-pid=\"u6ivlm-K\">这种方法对于项目的投资和维持阶段来说似乎是很有前景的，但是我有几点担心之处：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"hpqj8LgU\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z3rEZt3xPydnucv4Um8NTtRQY6P3uqTuvHso9\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">人们通常不能可靠地评估早期研究</a><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"9-IW0wYi\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z8EJnm4CKy2n2YKhByeZdv76D3vRHjsJL8WpV\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">二次方募资缺少在预案前工作方面对研究者的补偿</a> <br/> </li></ul><hr/><p data-pid=\"nDYrpG8w\">2020/09/09 此话题的推特风暴：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//twitter.com/andy_matuschak/status/1303759634331701248\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">twitter.com/andy_matusc</span><span class=\"invisible\">hak/status/1303759634331701248</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><h2>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"FfsiGJ1n\">暂无</li></ul><h2>声明</h2><p data-pid=\"a1kSLiu9\">此内容发布由 Andy Matuschak 许可。未经允许，不得转载或修改。保留所有权利。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"WqL_T9g6\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 <span class=\"nolink\">Lucas-Tsui</span>、校对 Shom<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z2znyciwTKuthTj6cReuPpHX37odgwjvTZrWG\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">To what extent can quadratic funding provision tools for thought? (andymatuschak.org)</a></blockquote>",
